summary: These documents pertain to Project LIENVOY, a sensitive intelligence operation. They include monthly operational reports, production reports, and personality briefs. The reports cover target lines, processing of information, exploitation of leads, liaison activities, security, technical issues, personnel, and production metrics. Noteworthy individuals such as Lazaro Cardenas del Rio and David Alfaro Siqueiros are profiled. The documents also discuss interactions with Cuban and Soviet officials and operations against various targets including embassies and political figures.
title: LIENVOY Operations - Monthly Operational and Production Reports; Personality Briefs
